18
00:02:49,750 --> 00:02:51,083
{\an8}Sorry about the wait.

19
00:02:51,166 --> 00:02:53,250
{\an8}-He'll be right with you.
-Great.

20
00:02:53,333 --> 00:02:54,958
{\an8}-Come with me.
-Thank you.

21
00:02:55,958 --> 00:02:58,250
{\an8}-Have a good day.
-I'll come with you.

22
00:02:59,750 --> 00:03:00,750
{\an8}Please do.

23
