55
00:06:48,833 --> 00:06:51,208
Helsinki, go after him.

56
00:06:52,333 --> 00:06:54,125
-Look after her.
-My friend...

57
00:07:07,250 --> 00:07:10,333
From now on, the rules have changed.
Nobody gets up,

58
