Resistance, my ass.

77
00:08:12,083 --> 00:08:14,666
Everyone, on the fucking ground now!

78
00:08:27,125 --> 00:08:28,500
That's right, Sergio.

79
00:08:28,833 --> 00:08:31,708
We need to know
how the bodyguards will react.

80
00:08:32,291 --> 00:08:33,625
How they react,

81
